174
00:12:49,335 --> 00:12:52,270
ROSLlN: But certainly
there'd be heavy damage,

175
00:12:52,338 --> 00:12:54,932
and you'd take
significant casualties.

176
00:12:55,008 --> 00:12:58,535
So you can go out there
and fight it out
with Galactica,

177
00:12:58,611 --> 00:13:00,408
or you can compromise.

178
00:13:00,547 --> 00:13:04,347
And those are
the only two options
on the table, period.

179
00:13:09,756 --> 00:13:13,556
How the two of you
have survived this long,
I will never know.

180
00:13:15,795 --> 00:13:20,198
All right. Lt. Thrace
has sent me detailed
recon information

181
00:13:20,266 --> 00:13:22,757
on the Cylon fleet.
I want that fleet.

182
00:13:22,835 --> 00:13:25,770
And I need Galactica
to get it. So I'm willing
to go this far.

183
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:29,704
I'll suspend the executions
until after the attack.

184
00:13:29,876 --> 00:13:31,537
I want them back on Galactica.

185
