the attack on this fleet.

198
00:14:58,931 --> 00:15:00,990
Now, I thought
Stinger was that man,

199
00:15:01,067 --> 00:15:03,160
but he managed to let
Capt. Adama contact you

200
00:15:03,236 --> 00:15:05,397
and pull off that fly-by stunt
right under his nose,

201
00:15:05,471 --> 00:15:06,904
so he's out.

202
00:15:08,207 --> 00:15:10,107
