203
00:15:12,211 --> 00:15:15,942
Truth be told,
I came this close
to throwing him in the brig,

204
00:15:16,816 --> 00:15:18,841
but I couldn't exactly
charge him and not you,

205
00:15:18,918 --> 00:15:21,580
so I've just revoked
his flight status.

206
00:15:25,191 --> 00:15:27,284
I want him on my team, sir.

207
00:15:38,971 --> 00:15:41,098
