get what you want?

208
00:15:43,109 --> 00:15:45,441
Most of the time, sir.

209
00:15:46,412 --> 00:15:47,504
Good.

210
00:15:49,615 --> 00:15:50,809
Me, too.

211
00:15:56,422 --> 00:15:57,753
All right, you can have him.

212
00:15:59,492 --> 00:16:02,017
