that our ultimate goal

218
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:19,471
is that we should return
to the 12 Colonies

219
00:16:19,545 --> 00:16:21,638
and kick the Cylons
the frak out of our homes.

220
00:16:24,283 --> 00:16:26,183
