throughout this sector.

486
00:38:24,636 --> 00:38:27,935
Our plan, simply put,
is to let them find us.

487
00:38:28,907 --> 00:38:31,239
We will wait
in this system here,

488
00:38:31,309 --> 00:38:34,335
and appear to be conducting
mining operations.

