00:38:36,114 --> 00:38:38,810
Galactica and most
of the civilians
will jump away.

491
00:38:38,917 --> 00:38:41,317
A small group of civilians
will be left behind.

492
00:38:41,386 --> 00:38:43,616
To the Cylons,
they'll appear
to be having trouble

493
00:38:43,688 --> 00:38:47,647
with their FTL drives
and attempting to escape
at sub-light speed.

