00:38:54,999 --> 00:38:58,059
APOLLO: Once the Raiders have
been drawn off by the decoys,

497
00:38:58,403 --> 00:39:02,499
Galactica and Pegasus
will jump in and attack
the Base Stars,

498
00:39:04,042 --> 00:39:08,001
while I jump in
in the Blackbird
stealth fighter

499
00:39:08,146 --> 00:39:09,943
and take out the FTL drives

500
00:39:10,014 --> 00:39:12,482
on the Resurrection ship,
preventing it
from jumping away.

501
00:39:12,684 --> 00:39:16,381
Why not have the stealth ship
carry nukes and destroy it
right at the start?

502
00:39:16,454 --> 00:39:19,753
We ran simulations on that.
We determined
that the Cylons would detect

503
00:39:19,824 --> 00:39:21,883
the nuclear warheads
and destroy the stealth ship

504
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:24,394
before it got
within weapons range.

505
00:39:24,963 --> 00:39:29,229
When the FTL is destroyed,
Galactica and Pegasus

506
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:31,063
will take on the Base Stars,

507
00:39:31,136 --> 00:39:34,628
and our attack squadrons
will go after the Resurrection
ship itself.

508
00:39:35,206 --> 00:39:36,901
How many squadrons?

509
00:39:38,977 --> 00:39:40,001
All of them.

510
00:39:52,457 --> 00:39:53,947
Is there a problem,
Commander?

511
00:39:56,027 --> 00:39:59,121
I need time to study
the operational details.

512
00:40:00,698 --> 00:40:04,327
Suit yourself.
I've gone over the details
and I'm satisfied.

513
00:40:05,203 --> 00:40:09,264
I want your CAG to stay
and help me answer
some of my questions.

514
00:40:11,509 --> 00:40:13,101
One hour, Thrace.

515
00:40:13,178 --> 00:40:14,440
Yes, sir.

516
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:23,681
Stay focused, son.

517
00:40:41,339 --> 00:40:45,207
Jack, I want to transfer
a detachment of Marines
to Galactica.

518
00:40:46,544 --> 00:40:48,842
And I want you
to hand-pick them.

519
00:40:50,481 --> 00:40:54,212
Completely reliable.
Completely loyal.

520
00:40:55,887 --> 00:40:56,876
Razors.

521
00:40:57,722 --> 00:40:59,952
I have a mission for you,
Kara.

522
00:41:00,725 --> 00:41:02,158
Anything for you.
You know that.

523
00:41:03,461 --> 00:41:05,452
Don't accept too quickly.

524
00:41:06,397 --> 00:41:07,864
You won't like this one.

525
00:41:10,168 --> 00:41:11,192
I don't like it.

526
00:41:13,104 --> 00:41:15,800
But I've decided
that it has to be done.

527
00:41:16,574 --> 00:41:18,667
I'm transferring you
to Galactica as well.

528
00:41:20,211 --> 00:41:23,612
I'll tell Adama that
you're there to be
my eyes and ears.

529
00:41:24,382 --> 00:41:27,579
He'll hate it,
he'll think you're my spy

530
00:41:27,652 --> 00:41:29,950
and try to freeze you out
of decision-making,

531
00:41:31,089 --> 00:41:32,750
but he'll accept it.

532
00:41:33,124 --> 00:41:36,616
Now, I want you to stay
in ClC throughout the attack.

533
00:41:36,694 --> 00:41:39,060
Stay with Adama.

534
00:41:39,130 --> 00:41:41,564
ADAMA: After the attack
is completed,

535
00:41:42,066 --> 00:41:44,626
and you've accounted
for your pilots,

536
00:41:45,103 --> 00:41:48,504
I want you to land your bird
on the Pegasus to report

537
00:41:48,606 --> 00:41:50,198
directly to ClC.

538
00:41:52,410 --> 00:41:54,401
You'll take Lee with you.

539
00:41:54,846 --> 00:41:56,336
He'll watch your back.

540
00:41:56,414 --> 00:41:59,508
Position Marines
in key areas throughout
the ship and keep a squad

541
00:41:59,584 --> 00:42:01,518
posted just outside ClC.

542
00:42:01,586 --> 00:42:04,817
Now, there will be the normal
chaos and emotional high
after the attack.

543
00:42:04,889 --> 00:42:07,949
They'll be slapping
each other on the back,
celebrating the victory.

544
00:42:08,026 --> 00:42:09,050
That'll keep their guard down.

545
00:42:09,127 --> 00:42:10,924
Security will be lax.

546
00:42:13,765 --> 00:42:16,700
I will ask for you
over the wireless.

547
00:42:17,101 --> 00:42:19,763
I will call you directly.
And when I have you
on the line

548
00:42:19,837 --> 00:42:23,534
and you hear me
give the command "Execute
case orange"...

549
00:42:23,875 --> 00:42:25,809
When you hear me
say "Downfall"...

550
00:42:28,413 --> 00:42:32,315
...you are to signal
the Marines to terminate
Adama's command.

551
00:42:34,752 --> 00:42:36,515
Start it with Adama.

552
00:42:38,756 --> 00:42:40,781
...I want you
to pull out your weapon

553
00:42:42,427 --> 00:42:44,861
and shoot Adm. Cain
in the head.

